@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Approved
Approved --> Reviewed : review
Reviewed --> Rejected : reject
Rejected --> Closed : cancel
Rejected : entry / log assignment
Closed --> Delivered : process
Closed : entry / log assignment
Rejected --> Closed : revert
Delivered --> [*]
@enduml